reviewText: Good price ,combining 6 DVDs ... excellent! The product came in excellent condiction. Will keep using the matierial forever. MJ
Anthony Robbins,can't say enough about what this man does, with his programs. I haven't found a program that isn't good to listen to.

Its a good overview of Tony's view on Alkalinity and its effects. But there's not much else in the program and almost nothing new from his earlier products. However its a good (and fairly inexpensive) intro on Tony's material on wellness in general
